---
// FootyGuess Daily Landing Page
---

<div
  class="relative w-full bg-gradient-to-br from-green-900 via-emerald-900 to-teal-900 overflow-y-auto"
>
  <div class="relative max-w-6xl mx-auto p-4 sm:p-8">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <div
      class="backdrop-blur-xl bg-gradient-to-b from-white/10 to-white/5 rounded-2xl shadow-2xl p-8 sm:p-12 text-white border border-white/10 mb-8"
    >
      <div class="text-center space-y-6">
        <h1
          class="text-5xl sm:text-7xl font-bold bg-gradient-to-r from-green-200 via-emerald-200 to-teal-200 text-transparent bg-clip-text drop-shadow-lg"
        >
          ‚öΩ FootyGuess Daily
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl sm:text-2xl text-green-100/90 drop-shadow-md max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Test your football knowledge! Guess the location and year of iconic football moments.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Game Modes -->
    <div
      class="backdrop-blur-xl bg-gradient-to-b from-white/10 to-white/5 rounded-2xl shadow-2xl p-8 sm:p-12 text-white border border-white/10"
    >
      <h2
        class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold mb-8 text-center text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-green-200 to-emerald-200"
      >
        Choose Your Mode
      </h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <!-- Normal Mode -->
        <div
          class="bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-900/30 to-blue-800/20 backdrop-blur-lg rounded-xl p-8 border border-blue-400/20 flex flex-col"
        >
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
            <div class="text-3xl">üéÆ</div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-200">Normal Mode</h3>
          </div>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-blue-100/80 mb-6 flex-grow">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="mr-2">‚Ä¢</span>
              <span>Play unlimited rounds anytime</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="mr-2">‚Ä¢</span>
              <span>Practice and improve your skills</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="mr-2">‚Ä¢</span>
              <span>Results shown immediately</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="mr-2">‚Ä¢</span>
              <span>Scores not saved to leaderboard</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
          <a
            href="/play/normal"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 whitespace-nowrap rounded-md text-sm font-medium transition-all h-12 px-6 bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-500 text-white shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transform hover:scale-105 active:scale-95"
          >
            Play Normal Mode
          </a>
        </div>

        <!-- Daily Mode -->
        <div
          class="bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-900/30 to-orange-800/20 backdrop-blur-lg rounded-xl p-8 border border-amber-400/20 flex flex-col relative overflow-hidden"
        >
          <div class="absolute top-4 right-4 bg-amber-500 text-amber-950 text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-full">
            COMPETE
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
            <div class="text-3xl">üèÖ</div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-amber-200">Daily Mode</h3>
          </div>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-amber-100/80 mb-6 flex-grow">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="mr-2">‚Ä¢</span>
              <span>New challenge every day at 00:00 UTC</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="mr-2">‚Ä¢</span>
              <span>5 unique photos never used before</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="mr-2">‚Ä¢</span>
              <span>First attempt counts for Top-10 leaderboard</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="mr-2">‚Ä¢</span>
              <span>Compete with players worldwide</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
          <a
            href="/play/daily"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 whitespace-nowrap rounded-md text-sm font-medium transition-all h-12 px-6 bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-600 to-orange-600 hover:from-amber-500 hover:to-orange-500 text-white shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transform hover:scale-105 active:scale-95"
          >
            Play Daily Challenge
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Footer Note -->
      <p class="text-center mt-8 text-green-100/60 text-sm max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Daily mode requires a nickname for the leaderboard. Your first attempt each day is recorded. You can replay as
        many times as you want!
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
